 Pod - Attribute Value Editor

 To  edit a  value,  put  the cursor  into the 
 window containing the  value that you wish to
 modify. Then edit as normal with the keyboard.
 
 Recognized commands are:-

    <Ctrl> n     Move forward a character.
    <Ctrl> b     Move back a character.
    <Ctrl> a     Move to start of text
    <Ctrl> k     Kill to end of line.

